🌅 Surah Al-Falaq

📘 Surah ka Taruf:
➡️Surah Al-Falaq Qur’an ki aakhri 2 suraton (Mu‘awwidhatayn) me se ek hai.
   Isko "protection ki surah" 🛡️ bhi kaha jata hai kyunki ye hume har qisam ke shar (bure asraat) se 
  Allah ki panah maanghne ki taleem deti hai.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌟 Ahmiyat:
➡️ Nabi ﷺ ne farmaya ke in dono suraton (Al-Falaq aur An-Naas) se Allah ki hifazat talabi jaye,
   aur aap ﷺ roz subh 🌅, shaam 🌙 aur sote waqt 😴 inhe parh kar apne upar dum karte the.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📖 Mazmoon:
    Surah ka aghaaz “Qul” se hota hai, matlab “Keh do (ya Muhammad ﷺ)”.
    Yani- hume bhi sikhaaya ja raha hai ke Allah se sidha madad maangho 🤲.

Is surah me Allah se 4 qisam ke shar se panah maangi gayi hai:

1️⃣ Raat ke andheron 🌌 ka shar – jab log gumrahi aur shayateen ka asar ziada hota hai.
2️⃣ Jadoo ✨ (sihr) karne walon ka shar – jo ghaat lagate hain aur dusron ko nuqsan pohchate hain.
3️⃣ Hasad 💔 karne walon ka shar – jo dusron ki ni’maton par jalan rakhte hain.
4️⃣ Khalq ki buraaiyon 👥 ka shar – yani makhlooq ke ander jo burai paayi jaati hai.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

💡 Paigham:
➡️Ye surah hume samjhati hai ke insaan kitna bhi taqatwar ho 💪, magar asli hifazat sirf Allah hi karta hai 🕌.
   Insaan ko hamesha Allah ki panah talab karni chahiye, khaaskar andheron, jadoo, buri nazar 👁️‍🗨️ aur hasad se.

_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

📌 Lesson for us:
✔️ Har musalmaan ko apni zindagi ke har qadam par Allah se panah maangni chahiye 🤲.
✔️ Jalne 🔥, jalan karne, aur dusron ke nuqsan ki sochnay se bacha rehna chahiye.
✔️ Roz marra ki duaon me is surah ka parhna apni roohani hifazat 🕊️ ke liye bohot zaroori hai.

✨ Ek jumle me:
➡️Surah Al-Falaq Allah ki ek azeem dua hai jo hume duniya ki chaar bari buraiyon 
   (🌌 andhera, ✨ jadoo, 💔 hasad, 👥 makhlooq ka shar) se bachati hai.
